
        LRunnable[] run = new LRunnable[1];
        run[0] = ((LRunnable) (n)->{
            boolean b = (n%2!=0);
            display.setGlowing(b);
            Common.runTaskLater(run[0], 12L);
        }).loop(4).whenDone(display::remove);
        run[0].run();


is equivalent to:



loop 4 times:
  set {_b} to mod(b,2)!=0?true:false # or whatever ternary operator skript uses havent used it long time
  set {_display}'s glowing to {_b} # or whatever syntax it is
  wait 12 ticks
kill {_display}
